{
    "model": "kitchen.recipe",
    "pk": 2,
    "fields": {
        "name": "Beef Stew with Tomatoes",
        "instructions": "1. Prepare the beef\r\nCut the beef into chunks.\r\nPut it into cold water, bring to a boil, and remove the foam.\r\nTake the beef out and rinse it clean.\r\n\r\n2. Prepare the tomatoes\r\nCut the tomatoes into wedges.\r\n(You can peel them if you want a smoother texture.)\r\n\r\n3. Heat oil in a pot.\r\nAdd ginger and garlic, stir-fry until fragrant.\r\n\r\n4. Cook the beef\r\nAdd the beef and stir-fry for a few minutes.\r\nAdd soy sauce and dark soy sauce, mix well.\r\n\r\n5. Add tomatoes and simmer\r\nAdd the tomatoes and stir briefly.\r\nPour in water until the beef is covered.\r\nAdd sugar and optional spices (star anise, bay leaves).\r\n\r\n6. Slow cook\r\nBring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 60–90 minutes\r\nuntil the beef becomes tender.\r\n\r\n7. Season and serve\r\nAdd salt to taste.\r\nSprinkle spring onions on top if you like.\r\nServe hot.",
        "difficulty": "medium",
        "cook_time": 100,
        "image_url": "https://assets.tmecosys.com/image/upload/t_web_rdp_recipe_584x480/img/recipe/ras/Assets/93e13752-2074-4a51-9531-ccef35ff864c/Derivates/b5f11b67-e098-4983-9830-a5da45379bfc.jpg"
    }
},
{
    "model": "kitchen.recipe",
    "pk": 3,
    "fields": {
        "name": "Oatmeal with Milk",
        "instructions": "1. Heat the milk\r\nPour the milk into a small pot and heat it over medium-low heat.\r\nDo not let it boil too hard.\r\n\r\n2. Add oats\r\nAdd the oats into the warm milk.\r\nStir gently to prevent sticking.\r\n\r\n3. Cook\r\nCook for about 3–5 minutes, stirring occasionally,\r\nuntil the oats become soft and creamy.\r\n\r\n4. Sweeten\r\nAdd sugar or honey if you like a sweeter taste.\r\n\r\n5. Add toppings\r\nTurn off the heat.\r\nAdd sliced fruits and nuts on top.\r\n\r\n6. Serve\r\nLet it cool slightly, then enjoy.",
        "difficulty": "easy",
        "cook_time": 10,
        "image_url": "https://images.openai.com/static-rsc-3/mtMqtTr_34RGgMARwCOaHbI6f73xAh7R6fgdeMsDka79nvH3bwOTrCDaXMV4VdHM5_eboabbzJQrUofhcOJ2NNJV7Yr9pvYqqFjBjWAy_cE?purpose=fullsize&v=1"
